OL,3,CWhy are the US-Iran talks in Islamabad
OL,4,Cso important?
OL,6,FIt is a glorious day here in Tehran.
OL,7,FBlue skies and birdsong, the most
OL,8,Fperfect of spring mornings.
OL,10,FIt is also one of the most
OL,11,Fconsequential days for this country
OL,12,Fand indeed the world. The importance
OL,13,Fof the talks taking place in Islamabad
OL,14,Fcannot be underestimated.
OL,16,FUpon them rest lives and peace across
OL,17,Fa region, the global economy and the
OL,18,Fstyle of life for billions of people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
