OL,3,CWhy are the US-Iran talks in Islamabad
OL,4,Cso important?
OL,6,FThe Iranians flew to Islamabad on a
OL,7,Fcommercial plane; the presidential one
OL,8,Fwas blown up in this war. On the empty
OL,9,Fseats, photos of the children killed
OL,10,Fby American missiles in the Minab
OL,11,Fschool massacre. The "Great Satan" has
OL,12,Fmany faces for the Iranians.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
