OL,3,CWhy are the US-Iran talks in Islamabad
OL,4,Cso important?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIt may not be a popular narrative, but
OL,12,Fthese talks have incorporated many of
OL,13,FIran's demands. The Vice President, JD
OL,14,FVance, was their request, deemed less
OL,15,Fhawkish on this war. And they will
OL,16,Fonly go ahead if some sort of deal on
OL,17,FLebanon is included, another Iranian
OL,18,Fdemand.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
