OL,3,CWhy are the US-Iran talks in Islamabad
OL,4,Cso important?
OL,6,FIf they fail, it is likely war will
OL,7,Fresume. Iran will find itself under
OL,8,FAmerican and Israeli bombardment once
OL,9,Fmore. But they are ready for that, and
OL,10,FIran has proved, as it has before,
OL,11,Fthat it absorbs and adapts. If bombing
OL,12,Fwas going to bring change, it would
OL,13,Fhave by now.
OL,15,FThe President says Iran has no cards.
OL,16,FIt does, and it's a big one, the
OL,17,FStrait of Hormuz and all that waterway
OL,18,Fmeans for the world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
